				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: High lvl SKs<a name="55403"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 9:11 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The secret to SK's is that they have a limited mana pool. Their unresistable tap is not mana effecient, and if you can get 500 to all resists you will bounce at least half the spears.
<br />

<br />
I like to just manadrain, keep marr and niv's up to eat some of the tap and play the draining game. With a good horn (or just use puretone) you can drain them dry fairly fast. You can try dispelling but with enough instant clicks they will be safe since their spells cast so quickly.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
